thread.title: Court indefinitely suspends disgraced Strongsville attorney tied to Cuyahoga County corruption figure
thread.title_full: Court indefinitely suspends disgraced Strongsville attorney tied to Cuyahoga County corruption figure

author: Cory Shaffer, cleveland.com
title: Court indefinitely suspends disgraced Strongsville attorney tied to Cuyahoga County corruption figure
text: The Ohio Supreme Court has indefinitely suspended the law license of Marc Doumbas, who was convicted of felony bribery charges alongside Cuyahoga County corruption figure Anthony Calabrese III.
